entries.title_d: The crystal smuggler apparently had a squad of fighters watching over it. Destroy all of those fighters and make sure you secure those crystals.
entries.title: Dathomir System: Destroy the Mercenary Ambush
entries.split_quest_alert: Whatever that smuggler had, someone wants it back badly. Deliver the contents to our transport shuttle.
entries.complete: You have survived the Suprise Attack!
